neosnatch (0.7.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release pipeline fixes for v0.7.0 multi-distro launch:
    - Add MIT LICENSE file at repo root (referenced by README and bundled
      into the static-musl tarball).
    - build-rpm.sh + release.yml locate the .rpm under
      target/<triple>/generate-rpm when cross-compiling (cargo-generate-rpm
      writes there, not target/generate-rpm).

